{"tid":1478363,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［持久戰心態］即使星期日出黎無50萬人 我地都唔應該覺得少左人支持我地","createTime":"2019-08-16T13:17:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T04:46:10.000Z","uid":41389,"like":58,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"b3ecb5d2219cd4028bb2bf8388d3ed2471f45793","tid":1478363,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:17:39.000Z","msg":"以前和非力咁出力出黎 係因為出到黎都係無包袱<br />\n帶埋一家大細連bb仔都帶埋出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但而家犬出反對通知書 好大可能又出催淚彈同鳩捉人 有要養家既和理非唔出黎都唔係無道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住社會上有好多人係背後出力支持緊我地 <br />\n有義務律師 有家長開車 有物資部 有攬炒隊 有文宣部 有大戶巴打 好多好多唔同既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要記住我地係一班3個鐘就可以籌到2M USD既人<br />\n我地係一班可以將香港呢兩隻字帶到國際層面既人<br />\n而家支共打壓越勁 就越證明我地既威脅越黎越大<br />\n<br />\n人少的確係我地既缺點 所以我地更加唔應該送頭<br />\n我地既聲線只會越黎越大 而共狗既死期將會越黎越近 當我地越覺得會輸 敵人既反攻越勁 就證明我地步向緊勝利 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者對於一班唔敢同狗肉搏既人對前線最大既支持 就係繼續係唔同戰線戰鬥 做更加多好既文宣 繼續入美金禁錢 繼續搵仔 開學罷課得閒又罷下市罷下工 外國戰線繼續高舉象徵和平既旗 亦不忘繼續將革命滲透共國之內 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n短期戰線我地起碼捱到9月美國國會復會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n面對強權 我地更加要智勝 以柔制剛 鄰國不斷逼商家表態想割斷我地背後既力量 但我地核彈都不割 前線做咩都唔割 做錯就要糾正 唔好比憤怒遮眼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學天琦話 革命要等十年八成功無可厚非 請各位香港人繼續戰鬥 宗旨係唔割席 唔送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc4b3db757676f6058e7cca3ecb7f70170b88c6f","tid":1478363,"uid":41389,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:20:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xgDvj7t.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxgDvj7t.gif&h=17a7f612&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9066c28109f6fda998114381b21b66aa82b60f6","tid":1478363,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"225f0b1b576343b2966f75350b531c838ace52c2","tid":1478363,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:22:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a74c277813dedcf08fd98265709e963a760a35d2","tid":1478363,"uid":193371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:22:59.000Z","msg":"推818"},{"pid":"c84997a0bd41575c1c9f232bb2ea5e6f833d2ced","tid":1478363,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:23:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07b51a08fda8a80159caf27bd92cbccb8b57c732","tid":1478363,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc4b3db757676f6058e7cca3ecb7f70170b88c6f","tid":1478363,"uid":41389,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:20:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xgDvj7t.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxgDvj7t.gif&h=17a7f612&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:23:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf5b96b24fb47b40dc63c764624d2e9d1d96a3c9","tid":1478363,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:24:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xgDvj7t.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"http